						 <p>I like this but can't upvote it, because it strays too close being a story that the Foundation wouldn't have access to. I get that this is Kristiansen's punishment in Hell, or something along those lines, but as a result it just isn't really something the Foundation would record. Unless Kristiansen's Hell is a little subdimension that the Foundation can keep their eyes on, then where exactly is this surveilance footage and test logs coming from?</p> 
