					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13398162#post-4674807</guid>
				<title>+1</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13398162/scp-5683#post-4674807</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 03 Jun 2020 07:32:36 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Alfadillo Gonadicus</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4314049</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>My guy, you nearly lost me with &quot;SCP-5683 is to be neutralized as soon as possible&quot; but the 74 upvotes kept me intrigued and I have to say, I'm glad I stuck around.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;SPOILERS</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;I&nbsp;hope&nbsp;you&nbsp;read&nbsp;the&nbsp;document&nbsp;first</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>I would have to assume 5683 is Kristansen's permanent reminder of how he died at the hands of 682. I'm guessing you wanted the <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-5682">5682</a> slot but it was already taken?</p> </div> </div> </div> <p><em>Also</em>, <em>I've noticed you've been writing a lot more lately</em>, <em>keep it up</em>!</p> <hr /> <p>I noticed a minor mistake, in &quot;Discussion Log 5683-3&quot; the &quot;Subject of Discussion:&quot; reads &quot;Termination SCP-5683&quot;. I would assume you meant &quot;<em>of</em> SCP-5683&quot;?</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
